  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Ladybright\" title=\"House Ladybright\"><img alt=\"None (Dorne).svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/44/None_%28Dorne%29.svg/50px-None_%28Dorne%29.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/44/None_%28Dorne%29.svg/75px-None_%28Dorne%29.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/44/None_%28Dorne%29.svg/100px-None_%28Dorne%29.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Jayne Ladybright</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Ladybright\" title=\"House Ladybright\"><img alt=\"None (Dorne).svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/44/None_%28Dorne%29.svg/50px-None_%28Dorne%29.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/44/None_%28Dorne%29.svg/75px-None_%28Dorne%29.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/44/None_%28Dorne%29.svg/100px-None_%28Dorne%29.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Jayne_Ladybright_by_Sabotensan.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Jayne Ladybright by Sabotensan.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/89/Jayne_Ladybright_by_Sabotensan.jpg/350px-Jayne_Ladybright_by_Sabotensan.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"467\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/89/Jayne_Ladybright_by_Sabotensan.jpg/525px-Jayne_Ladybright_by_Sabotensan.jpg 1.5x, /images/8/89/Jayne_Ladybright_by_Sabotensan.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Jayne Ladybright by Sabotensan ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Ladybright\" title=\"House Ladybright\">House Ladybright</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornish\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dornish\">Dornish</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Jayne Ladybright</b> is <a href=\"/index.php/Dornish\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dornish\">Dornish</a> noblewoman from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Ladybright\" title=\"House Ladybright\">House Ladybright</a>. Her relation to <a href=\"/index.php/Alyse_Ladybright\" title=\"Alyse Ladybright\">Alyse Ladybright</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Sunspear\" title=\"Sunspear\">Sunspear</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_treasurer\" title=\"Lord treasurer\">Lord treasurer</a>, is unknown.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#The_Winds_of_Winter\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jayne_Ladybright&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Jayne is pretty.<sup id=\"cite_ref-sample_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-sample-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jayne_Ladybright&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jayne_Ladybright&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Jayne accompanies Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a> on her mission to meet <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">Stormlands</a>. On the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Peregrine\" title=\"Peregrine\">Peregrine</a></i> Jayne is <a href=\"/index.php/Greensick\" title=\"Greensick\">greensick</a> and spends most of the voyage vomiting, which <a href=\"/index.php/Elia_Sand\" title=\"Elia Sand\">Elia Sand</a> finds hilarious.<sup id=\"cite_ref-sample_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-sample-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jayne_Ladybright&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-sample-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-sample_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-sample_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_I_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Arianne I (The Winds of Winter)\">The Winds of Winter, Arianne I</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a 